USAGE: rcup.py [-h] [-Ha] <USER> <PASS>

This script can update rcfiles on NAO and/or hardfought.org; default behavior is
to update NAO and to update hardfought, but this can be modified by the options
listed in the next section.

OPTIONS:
    -h,-?,--help                Display this information

    -H,--hdf,--hardfought       Enable hardfought.org (default)

    --no-hdf,--no-hardfought    Disable hardfought.org

    -a,--nao,--altorg           Enable nethack.alt.org (default)

    --no-nao,--no-altorg        Disable nethack.alt.org


